Siemens - Wikipedia





















 






Siemens

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about a German engineering company. For the former Fujitsu-Siemens company, see Fujitsu Siemens Computers. For other uses, see Siemens (disambiguation).

Siemens AG





Type

Aktiengesellschaft


Traded as
FWB: SIE
DAX Component


Industry
Conglomerate


Founded
12 October 1847; 169 years ago (1847-10-12)
Berlin, Kingdom of Prussia


Founder
Werner von Siemens


Headquarters
Berlin and Munich, Germany



Area served

