					     MindSphere
				

























Singapore Digitalization Hub
Siemens partners with Singapore to establish its first fully-integrated Digitalization Hub. Powered by MindSphere – Siemens' cloud-based open IoT operating system, the Hub will drive digitalization in the country on its way to become a Smart Nation.

























MindSphere
The cloud-based, open IoT operating system from Siemens. For the digital transformation of companies regardless of industry or size. Implementable within a very short period of time.























